## Named Parameters

| Parameter | Type | Default | Purpose |
|-----------|------|---------|---------|
| `window_size` | INTEGER | 50 | Window size in variant count |
| `window_kb` | INTEGER | none | Window size in kilobases (overrides window_size) |
| `step` | INTEGER | 5 | Step size (variants to advance window) |
| `r2_threshold` | DOUBLE | 0.5 | Max r² before pruning |
| `pvar` | VARCHAR | auto-discovered | Explicit .pvar/.bim path |
| `psam` | VARCHAR | auto-discovered | Explicit .psam/.fam path |
| `samples` | LIST(VARCHAR) or LIST(INTEGER) | all | Filter to specific samples |
| `region` | VARCHAR | all | Filter to genomic region |

